metadata.name: #1 - Rain, Rain, Come Again!
metadata.description:
Rain is nothing but an ode of love from heaven to earth. Dia loves the rain. She also just learned the fact that we need trees to soak up that water into the earth. When asked why the girl needs an umbrella, she said the girl would like to play outside but it's a new dress so she doesn't want it to get wet.
